	   <tr><td colspan=2>If you want to bypass the Armour of Ro, head for Skyshrine in your early 40s. The Sentry and Guardian Armour are sooooo much better than Ro. Makes me wish I never bothered with the Ro in the first place. Heck, since you're levle 16 right now, by the time you're in your 30s you may be able to head to Skyshrine and loot some of the items since most are No Drop. Just buy some Invisibility Potions from a vendor (cost is about 10pp from the merchant near the Monk Guild in Freeport) and do your run through EWastes and Kael (just be careful since some of those Giants in Kael see through Invisibility).<br><br>&nbsp;<br>________<br><br>I've travelled this world and have seen many wondrous things. You are not one of them.</td></tr>
